SubjectMinisterial Declaration on the Expansion of Trade in Information Technology Products - World Trade Organization
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the necessary measures to bring into force, on behalf of Canada the MINISTERIAL DECLARATION ON THE EXPANSION OF TRADE IN INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY PRODUCTS, known as the expanded ITA, adopted at Nairobi on December 16, 2015.
